title: Storm signals up in 9 provinces as 'Auring' intensifies slightly
text: Storm signals up in 9 provinces as 'Auring' intensifies slightly (philstar.com)   5:41pm Auring is forecast to make landfall over the Surigao provinces between Sunday evening and early Monday morning. (PAGASA release) MANILA, Philippines -- Storm signals were raised over more provinces on Saturday afternoon as Tropical Depression "Auring" intensified slightly. In its 5 p.m. Severe Weather Bulletin, PAGASA said Auring now has maximum winds up to 55 kph and gustiness of up to 70 kph as it continues to move west northwest.
